1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 17=

11
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:07,680
Moving the sword
is already no easy feat.

12
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:09,760
Didn't expect...

13
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,040
Grandpa.

14
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,879
Hurry, bring him to me.

15
00:01:18,439 --> 00:01:19,719
(With skills like that,)

16
00:01:20,040 --> 00:01:21,959
(I can feel at ease)

17
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:23,280
(letting Tian stay with him.)

18
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,159
Was that

19
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,480
immortal light?

20
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:33,200
Su Wubing definitely has the makings
of an immortal.

21
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:35,560
(Though it's not fully refined yet,)

22
00:01:35,959 --> 00:01:37,120
(the immortal energy within)

23
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,840
(could help me recover my cultivation.)

24
00:01:40,159 --> 00:01:41,439
How did you make it?

25
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,079
(The moment the divine sword appeared,)

26
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:46,000
(I felt an aura similar
to my family heirloom)

27
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,799
(spirit stone.)

28
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,840
One thing.

29
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,280
Come back with me.

30
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,480
No way.

31
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,760
Come back with me.

32
00:01:57,079 --> 00:01:57,719
Grandpa is waiting.

33
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,280
I've already pulled the sword.

34
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,599
Your bet...

35
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,400
Impossible.

36
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:11,280
That doesn't count. You cheated.

37
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,400
Cheated? In front of everyone?

38
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,840
Is the Gu family trying to back out now?

39
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,400
Weren't you pretty arrogant just now?

40
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:22,599
Mr. Gu.

41
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,080
A bet is a bet.

42
00:02:35,039 --> 00:02:35,840
Su Wubing.

43
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,879
Just you wait.

44
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:41,280
Let's go.

45
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,319
Wubing.

46
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:05,199
This is my grandpa Fang Xianglin.

47
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,800
Grandpa, this is Su Wubing.

48
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,120
Have a seat.

49
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:15,080
You're very skilled.

50
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:18,639
Why have you stayed completely unknown

51
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:20,800
for the past twenty years?

52
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:24,120
Grandpa, he just doesn't like
showing off.

53
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,319
He's not hiding it on purpose.

54
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:28,280
I'm asking him, not you.

55
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,400
Some things are private.

56
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,439
I'd rather not say much.

57
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,960
But don't worry,

58
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,080
I'll always take care of Fang Tian.

59
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,280
With just that one sentence,

60
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:43,319
can I trust you with Tian?

61
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:46,039
That's a bit much to call trust.

62
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,199
Mr. Fang,

63
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:48,680
I was thinking

64
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:51,439
if you're really not at ease,

65
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:53,159
you should've taken Tian back.

66
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,039
Quick thinker, aren't you?

67
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:59,759
Tian, good eye.

68
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,840
This young man has a bright future.

69
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,000
Grandpa...

70
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:05,560
Since she is a member of your family,

71
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:07,639
why did you wait so long

72
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,199
to find her?

73
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,039
Wubing...

74
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,240
This is my fault.

75
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:16,439
Back then, with Fang family in chaos,

76
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,879
I had to send her away

77
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:21,000
to protect our bloodline.

78
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:22,839
All these years,

79
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:25,759
I've carried guilt in my heart.

80
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,800
I understand.

81
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,240
But whether she returns home,

82
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:31,319
it's up to her.

83
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:32,759
If she wants to go back,

84
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,040
I won't stop her.

85
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,560
If she wants to stay,

86
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,680
I'll keep taking care of her.

87
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,040
Alright.

88
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:41,279
With that, I'm relieved.

89
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,600
How about this.

90
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,879
When I go back,
I'll announce your marriage.

91
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,519
The wedding will be at the Fang family.

92
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,639
Grandpa, we're just like siblings.

93
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,120
Mr. Fang, you're joking, right?

94
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,480
What, you don't want it?

95
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:57,839
I have someone in my heart.

96
00:04:58,399 --> 00:04:59,600
I can't marry Tian.

97
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:04,199
Could it be that girl Lin Ningxue?

98
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:05,959
Mr. Fang,

99
00:05:07,959 --> 00:05:10,040
I've always treated Tian
like a little sister.

100
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,360
Either way,

101
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:13,000
I will continue to care for her.

102
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:14,800
Fine.

103
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,160
I won't meddle in

104
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,639
young people's affairs.

105
00:05:19,519 --> 00:05:20,839
The Fang family doors

106
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,319
will always be open for you.

107
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,920
Tian,

108
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:39,519
today I'll hand this bronze mirror
to you.

109
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:45,360
This mirror contains
ancient divine power.

110
00:05:46,639 --> 00:05:47,439
That's right.

111
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,480
This is

112
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,120
the Fang family's ancestral treasure.

113
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,439
Break it in a crisis,

114
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,040
and it can rewind time by one minute.

115
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,079
Whoever holds this mirror

116
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:02,800
is the head of the Fang family.

117
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:08,439
Today I formally pass it to Tian.

118
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,279
Come in.

119
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:23,759
You stole the spotlight
at the tournament.

120
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,959
Now the whole city knows

121
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:27,439
that my fiancé

122
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:29,480
is the one who pulled the divine sword.

123
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,199
I think it's a good thing.

124
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,639
At least from now on,

125
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,800
no one will dare mess
with the Lin family.

126
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,759
That's not what I want to say.

127
00:06:41,199 --> 00:06:44,639
Wedding crash, saving my dad
and drawing the sword?

128
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:47,000
You've got way too many secrets.

129
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:49,439
Su Wubing,

130
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,240
we've been through so much.

131
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:55,040
Can't you tell me the truth yet?

132
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,000
You may find hard to accept

133
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:05,240
every word I'm about to say,

134
00:07:06,439 --> 00:07:07,879
but it's all absolutely true.

135
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,720
You and I

136
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,759
were once immortal lovers.

137
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,279
But you're cursed by fate.

138
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,360
I once fought against the Heavenly Dao,

139
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,680
but in the end I couldn't save you.

140
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:30,519
So, I followed you
through reincarnation,

141
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:32,639
hiding from the Heavenly Dao.

142
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,920
You're saying

143
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:47,560
I still carry the Heavenly Dao's curse?

144
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:48,439
Then you...?

145
00:07:54,439 --> 00:07:54,839
Ningxue.

146
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,199
Ningxue.

147
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,319
Are you okay?

148
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:13,519
I'm fine. Just a sudden headache.

149
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:19,120
Take me for a walk.

150
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:26,439
So it's because you regained
your memories

151
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,519
that you found me.

152
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:32,919
Yes.

153
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:35,240
I didn't tell you before.

154
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,840
Afraid you wouldn't believe me

155
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,120
And I was afraid

156
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,679
the Heavenly Dao would notice.

157
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,919
So Mr. Ye calling you "My Lord"

158
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,960
was also from your past life?

159
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,039
Him?

160
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,799
He's my subordinate,

161
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,679
and waited ten thousand years.

162
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:01,639
So none of it was coincidence.

163
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:04,080
It's destiny.

164
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:06,519
Ningxue,

165
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:08,840
I don't want

166
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,639
to lose you again in this life.

167
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,840
What would happen
if you broke the curse?

168
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,240
Any attempt to break it

169
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,399
is seen by Heavenly Dao as a challenge.

170
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,720
The Heavenly Dao
will strike immediately

171
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,639
and destroy both of our spiritual forms.

172
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:42,240
I used to think

173
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,919
the Lin family matters

174
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,879
and my dad's illness
were all my burden alone.

175
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,440
Sometimes it pressed down on me.

176
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,879
I could barely breathe.

177
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,879
But after I met you,

178
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:59,320
I finally understood

179
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,440
what it feels like

180
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,919
to have someone to lean on.

181
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,919
Ever since my father
passed the responsibility to me,

182
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:13,360
I haven't had the right
to live like an ordinary person...

183
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,960
to date, to live.

184
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:18,320
I don't even know how to run a company.

185
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:20,320
But I know clearly

186
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,320
someone has to step up
at times like this.

187
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,720
Luckily,

188
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:30,879
I met you.

189
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,960
I'm not afraid of fate or duty or curse,

190
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,919
because I can now

191
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,320
stay with you like this.

192
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,120
Ningxue!

193
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,519
Ningxue...

194
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:14,879
My Lord.

195
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,399
Holy Maiden.

196
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:19,960
Mr. Ye, just call me by my name.

197
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:22,120
Why choose this place?

198
00:11:23,519 --> 00:11:24,919
The spiritual power is abundant here,

199
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,240
and Tianmiao has also set up a barrier.

200
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,720
If anything goes wrong,

201
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:32,159
Tianmiao can protect us.

202
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:35,720
Although you've retrieved
the Heavenly God Sword,

203
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,440
it still hasn't been refined.

204
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:41,600
I'm only one step away
from the Heavenly God Realm.

205
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:44,120
So what we can do now

206
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:46,039
is extend Ningxue's life.

207
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,279
Understood.

208
00:11:49,039 --> 00:11:50,960
Then let's not waste any time.

209
00:12:59,785 --> 00:13:03,888
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

210
00:13:03,888 --> 00:13:08,608
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

211
00:13:08,608 --> 00:13:13,488
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

212
00:13:13,488 --> 00:13:18,608
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

213
00:13:18,608 --> 00:13:23,008
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

214
00:13:23,008 --> 00:13:27,688
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

215
00:13:27,688 --> 00:13:33,088
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

216
00:13:33,088 --> 00:13:39,482
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
